.*
.* zblas — epilog.mac
.* Standard OS linkage epilogue for leaf BLAS routines.
.*
.* Usage:  EPILOG
.*
.* Restores R14-R12 from caller's save area and returns.
.* Float results already in FPR0. Integer results in R15.
.* No storage to free. We are leaf. We are simple. We are content.
.*
         MACRO
&LBL     EPILOG
&LBL     DS    0H
         LM    R14,R12,12(R13)             Restore all registers
         BR    R14                         Return to caller
         MEND
